## What It Does NOT Do

- ❌ Does **not** create audio devices (uses system audio API)
- ❌ Does **not** perform audio analysis (uses P1-A1 + P1-A2)
- ❌ Does **not** handle audio output (separate output module)
- ❌ Does **not** manage audio effects (use EffectManager)
- ❌ Does **not** provide audio recording (use Recorder module)
- ❌ Does **not** handle MIDI audio (use MIDIController)

