## Success Criteria

### Must Pass (All Required)

- [ ] Device enumeration completes in < 1 second
- [ ] All unit tests pass (≥80% coverage)
- [ ] Audio latency < 50ms with single device
- [ ] Automatic fallback works within 2 seconds of device loss
- [ ] Hot-plugging detection within 1 second
- [ ] Thread-safe: no race conditions in device management
- [ ] Works with at least 3 different audio devices
- [ ] Supports sample rates: 44.1kHz, 48kHz, 96kHz

### Should Pass (Best Effort)

- [ ] Multi-device support (2+ devices simultaneously)
- [ ] Sample rate conversion accuracy > 99%
- [ ] Device profiles save/load correctly
- [ ] Low-latency mode for live performance (< 20ms)
- [ ] Device status monitoring with health metrics

