## Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| Device enumeration fails on some systems | Medium | Medium | Fallback to default device, comprehensive error handling |
| Sample rate conversion artifacts | Low | Medium | High-quality conversion, configurable quality settings |
| Thread safety issues | Low | High | Lock-free design, atomic operations |
| Memory leaks from device handles | Low | Medium | Reference counting, cleanup on device removal |
| Platform differences (Windows/Linux/macOS) | High | Medium | Abstract audio backend, CI on all platforms |

